Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got two handshakes, I saw him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.43,0:01:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a couple of our favorites there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to say, your book has changed my life drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a fortune cookie for your collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My fortune cookie collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a fortune cookie message for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a fortune cookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, what about the side room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's people there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to come upstairs and say hello to all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we miss anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to miss anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've got to run, run, run, run, run, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, rabbit, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want help with the stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never regret the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You live to its fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll see if this is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to do to get the music to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a new fortune cookie just given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never regret the present if you live it to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated at 345, which is better than 90% of the world's literature, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A fortune cookie life is a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,345 is a good energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of enthusiasm and goodwill and things that are no longer fashionable,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but for spiritual people is certainly the beginning and the essence of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We always start the lecture with the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To a crowd like this, the intellect is the main problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Being cruel to your neighbors, lying routinely,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,cheating your employer is not usually a problem in a group like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Area addition is why people are here, because they have learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intellect, which then is how we learn about spiritual truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's where we get attracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it then eventually becomes the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the lectures have been considerably oriented towards
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,how to transcend the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How to transcend the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a humming noise. What's the humming noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That machine. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, modern life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You put up with hums and buzzes and .
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first moved away from the big city,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even stand the sound of a refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I literally unplugged the refrigerator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and lived in absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So how to transcend the limitations of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we're talking about positionality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,positionality and how to transcend positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fastest way is to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to jump the whole paradigm of the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how it is that things come in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,how it is that things happen in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we know that the Newtonian paradigm of reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of causality, the explanation of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sounds appealing, but it only calibrates around 450,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not exactly astronomical.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That means respectably intelligent and it's plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So causality violates, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the principle of post hoc ergo propter hoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because one thing follows another
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that that which preceded it is its cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, of course, the downside of modern society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So science, the world of the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration levels 450, 460,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, have been the great blessing to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather recent and evolutionary,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the intellect predominantly has only been really dominant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for, oh, 2,000 years or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is just barely yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So it still hasn't sunk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So large parts of the world calibrate, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,not only below the 400s, they calibrate below the 200s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the world's population calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And here in an audience like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is worrying about how to get through the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is a somewhat select group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So through the intellect, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we hear about spiritual reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and now our problem is how to transcend the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,how to experience reality without processing it sequentially
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,through the left brain and nominalizing everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,how to transcend the Newtonian paradigm of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what we've been doing is giving the lectures backwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and we find that's very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We start with the ending of how things actually come about,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the intellect figures out subsequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything happens of its own, of its own nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What you see happening is the consequence of the effect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are within a given context,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,within an infinite context, which we'll cover over the slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything comes about spontaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously as a consequence of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can picture everything and everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as though they're a magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This magnetic field draws to you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is of your own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing out there causing anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the downside of it in the broken window principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute there's a broken factory window in a neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't care, we're not responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the whole neighborhood goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing causes that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that that energy attracts mice,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cockroach, crime, drugs, prostitution,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,homicide, suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And degeneracy of one kind or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is attracting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As you let go of negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you become, you are that field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and you draw to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is a consequence of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything comes about as potentiality becoming actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You put that in a powerful field,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,now the potential actualizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the field, it's dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The seed lays there, the seed lays there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the rain, the warmth, and the sun comes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes, it doesn't force the seed to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but the seed of its own propensity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's its karmic potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,now responds to favorable conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and it shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing it to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:11:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not within the realm of cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Phenomena, then, are the consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of potentiality becoming actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,when the conditions are right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the infinite power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All that lives, lives within an infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,field of infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The slightest potentiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when put into a field of infinite power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the consequence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Without divinity, you have to resort
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Newtonian paradigm of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you picture divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what our research is all about,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there is an absolute non-variable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a giant electromagnetic field, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,everything within this field of infinite power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,aligns itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,according to that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the configuration,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where it happens to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's the karma of the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmic consequence, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a little iron filing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or a little molecule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Every decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,every action, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,affects the position
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of all these little molecules
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and this little iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shapes like this, it gets bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with good intention and it gets smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,with bad intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And where it is in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is the consequence of the infinite power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the field is not arbitrary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to an ignorant person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that gets pulled this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,blames it on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God condemns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you have the Old Testament
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of this capricious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of mentally ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering from paranoia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sensitivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,jealousy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,power,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and prone to favoritism,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,gets even with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty negative paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but it dominated society
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,until the present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that's pretty high caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to some other spiritual teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual, in quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings prevalent on the planet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All comes about as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to the realization of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is really the mystical pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really the way of non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Duality will limit you to the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the world of theology,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,epistemology, ontology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you don't dare cough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with a microphone on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm knocking my ears out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a jet plane going over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I said that, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In case I was wrong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a big, jealous, paranoid God,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and he does hate you, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so be it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we were created with intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we were created as spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of having been created in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,gifts us with an intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and a spiritual will,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and we then follow that spiritual will
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in blind faith
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and trust in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So the pathway of truth is what we teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional non-duality is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the way to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,avoiding the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and form of religion, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow through the pristine purity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to where it leads us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it leads us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and takes fortitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,takes inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,takes information,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,information,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which has traversed that pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And if one falters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,then I suggest the 91st Psalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the 91st Psalm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and you only need the one Psalm in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the 91st Psalm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Psalm also says that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord is one's fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and that his strength is his truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So the pathway of truth then does not violate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,old spiritual tradition either,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but merely puts it into operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who falters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a couple suggestions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you get a copy of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the military tattoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which was presented in Scotland
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,once a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or you watch Riverdance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're still depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,after watching Riverdance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or watching the Edinburgh Castle tattoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you do need a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when soul is somehow impaired,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be something obstructing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way to God then is through
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the joy of the present?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy of the present is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the full experience of the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of the source of one's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,one needs nothing outside oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing out there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The world insists that you eat things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and do all that kind of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Within yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you really don't need anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,being complete and total.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gets rid of wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,desiringness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,greed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and takes you out of the solar plexus
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we have a number of new people here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,who have not been to the lectures before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wowie, wowie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's more people upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we always say something new at every lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a new slide,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very instructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And we also recapitulate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what's been said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But every time we recapitulate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you hear it differently,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,having heard it once before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you become different than you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody here has ever heard today's lecture before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of reading Power Versus Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same as started reading it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're all in the process
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of evolution of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us are exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are what we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the material may look familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it's never been really given before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've never said it before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,nor has the person in the chair ever heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So every moment is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,every moment is startlingly new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And every moment is excitingly inspirational.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have to keep a lid on myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to not get over-exuberant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we will recapitulate
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the slides,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time with a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to start with the newest slide at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do that with this spotter machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a spotter machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also have a new
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we'll start with the new slide,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because it demonstrates what we just got through saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been agonizing work for two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and passed out about 7 o'clock last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I think we finished the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it's the last thing I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But one thing we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was we correlated level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because this book had to do with looking at the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which was quite interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because back in the 70s when I left the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally ignored it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never read a book,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,never watched television,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't own a TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't own a TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't know President Reagan had been shot or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And now to do this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to recalibrate everything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was a grand tour of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated every writer, songs, music, movies, philosophies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,places, positions, spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,whoa, everything from the Eiffel Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to all the things I've forgotten about,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so what we did was we calibrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,correlated the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the rate of unemployment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, things are not caused externally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody forces you to throw trash on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody forces you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you choose to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, according to the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a rather astonishing correlation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:22:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At the level of consciousness, the higher levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment is zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of poverty is zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of happiness is about 100%,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.15,0:22:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality is almost zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how that guy even got in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these gurus that takes you for your money,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, got in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we see these levels here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,400 to 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have the world of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of unemployment is 2%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably collecting unemployment insurance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of poverty is 0.5%
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,due to having made a bad investment, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness rate is 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't all have 100% of everything, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rate of criminality is 2%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.81,0:22:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess would be white-collar crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably fall for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The temptation of all that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.29,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 2% in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,let's just see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's primarily white-collar crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everybody know Susan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody doesn't know Susan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When somebody gets that close to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't notice them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think she's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She is an other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, it's an other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The world sees you as separate from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we've probably got white-collar crime there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The 300s and the 300s,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment is 7%.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what percent of these people are just there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're collecting unemployment insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of that percent,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,60% are there because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,80%, 90%.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, probably 85%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are listed as unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're collecting unemployment insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment, you know, usually ends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when your unemployment insurance runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've earned it all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well stay in Florida another week
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and see your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it runs out, you go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So the 300s there, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,all this is very low.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when you get to the 200s,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,in the 200s,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,rate of unemployment is 8%,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.85,0:24:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and again, probably a good part of that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is just collecting unemployment insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.85,0:24:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of poverty, 1.5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect recently divorce has made a bad investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.85,0:24:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness rate, 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.89,0:24:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're beginning to see some decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of criminality, 9%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.72,0:24:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so far, we've been over calibration level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.72,0:24:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It means over 200 doesn't mean you're a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't mean you're a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.72,0:24:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you do things that in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.11,0:24:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,are reasonable, probable, or necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.53,0:25:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now what happens when we go from below 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.53,0:25:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 100s, you see the rate of employment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is now suddenly 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.98,0:25:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see a huge jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.40,0:25:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of poverty, 22%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.72,0:25:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness rate drops to 15%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.72,0:25:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of criminality now is about 50% of that population.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.51,0:25:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When you drop below 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.97,0:25:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to do the scale of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.97,0:25:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,next, between 50 and 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,between 50 and 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.67,0:25:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment is 75%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rate of poverty, 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.75,0:25:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is down to 2%.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:25:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.75,0:25:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of criminality has skyrocketed to 91%,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.95,0:26:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because criminality is almost the way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.10,0:26:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You always steal from your employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.10,0:26:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You always pay out your expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.46,0:26:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You always pick up whatever is not,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and nail down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.22,0:26:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get below 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.33,0:26:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get below 50,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.33,0:26:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.33,0:26:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,there aren't any human beings below 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.33,0:26:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in today's headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.63,0:26:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in yesterday's headlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.58,0:26:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployment, 97%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.66,0:26:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty, 65%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is supported by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.14,0:26:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness rate, 0%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.46,0:26:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Criminality is a lifestyle, 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.46,0:26:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.19,0:26:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the correlation,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.19,0:26:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,how nothing is causing anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.19,0:26:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.19,0:26:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then, manifests itself in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.18,0:26:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in this sort of a style.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.98,0:26:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing outside you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.98,0:27:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,causing you to do any of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.98,0:27:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all coming from who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.00,0:27:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of the decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.00,0:27:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you relate to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.14,0:27:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and your ability to comprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.14,0:27:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual reality, morality, and ethics,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or the lack thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.14,0:27:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.23,0:27:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.39,0:27:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So we started with the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.57,0:27:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So now we can go back to number uno.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.57,0:27:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have questions and answers later,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.00,0:27:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if anybody has any questions about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.00,0:27:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of sociologic theories
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.00,0:27:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that calibrate about 180 or 190,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.00,0:27:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which is always trying to find a blame
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.00,0:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or something kind of blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.00,0:27:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that talks about blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.00,0:27:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, is fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.96,0:27:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the field that potentiates
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.96,0:27:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,these kind of phenomena?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.96,0:27:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.27,0:27:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.27,0:27:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get to you later, Bushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.55,0:28:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he wants to be part of the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.42,0:28:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you want to be part of the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.54,0:28:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My ego's name is Ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.34,0:28:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he wants to be front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.73,0:28:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what he's supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to want to be front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to want to win all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.98,0:28:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to want to be better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.77,0:28:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to hate people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.77,0:28:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who cut in front of you in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.60,0:28:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll get to ego later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.60,0:28:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just want...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we started with,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.15,0:28:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the consequences of understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.15,0:28:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the map of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.15,0:28:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, they're quite profound
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.15,0:28:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in every major area of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.63,0:28:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Every major area of life, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.63,0:28:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is affected by a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.63,0:29:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So to just recapitulate it, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.63,0:29:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we looked at what life is like from 200 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.98,0:29:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We see a high rate of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,low rate of unemployment, low rate of crime, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.72,0:29:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we see at consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.72,0:29:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a really dramatic change.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.72,0:29:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we go from very low numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to extremely high numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We could spend the whole lecture just on this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.82,0:29:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I first devised this script,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.82,0:29:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,devised this scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was giving lectures at a rehab place,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.11,0:29:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we did spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.11,0:29:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd spend a couple hours on just this scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.11,0:29:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,discussing each level, discussing each level,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.11,0:29:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because recovery from a great many human conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.11,0:29:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,addictions being one of them, alcoholism,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.11,0:29:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and various others,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.15,0:29:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then is based on going above level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.63,0:30:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the first step in the 12-step program,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.63,0:30:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,any one in which you accept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.63,0:30:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you accept responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.85,0:30:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you're already on the way over level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.85,0:30:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the difficulty with blame,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to blame conditions on external conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is blame you instantly are divesting yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.85,0:30:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of responsibility, making yourself the helpless victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.85,0:30:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're instantly below level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.85,0:30:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Theories below 200 do not help the people below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.14,0:30:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for which the theory is devised in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.14,0:30:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it gets abused and misused and exploited.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.33,0:30:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, learning to be responsible then,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.91,0:30:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.91,0:30:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, I'm the one that said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.91,0:30:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll take the consequences for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.91,0:30:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.91,0:30:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes you over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.93,0:31:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens over 200 now
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.11,0:31:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is your, you might say, your magnetic charge changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.11,0:31:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you stop pulling rats, mice, cockroaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.47,0:31:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and various bad viruses into your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.73,0:31:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and you start pulling healing energies,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.73,0:31:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people with whom you congregate change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.73,0:31:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.72,0:31:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was director of a big rehab place
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.23,0:31:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,here in Arizona,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.42,0:31:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.42,0:31:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew already,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.42,0:31:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because I knew who they were hanging out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.80,0:31:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who they were hanging out with
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.80,0:31:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,told me exactly where they were at,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.48,0:31:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,whether they'd given up gang colors or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.19,0:31:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become different,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.19,0:31:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you live a different life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.19,0:31:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You hang out with different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.19,0:31:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think different thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.19,0:31:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have different standards and values.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.53,0:32:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, you're quite a bit different than the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.53,0:32:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the people above and below are really quite a bit different,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.74,0:32:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,remarkably different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.74,0:32:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you get to the lower levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.74,0:32:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.74,0:32:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for people above 200 to even comprehend that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.27,0:32:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and accept it as a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which is today's headlines, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.50,0:32:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The inability to comprehend that people literally
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.75,0:32:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,live in this level down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.14,0:32:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,below the level of the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.33,0:32:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend, the Komodo dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.33,0:32:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates around 40.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.33,0:32:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.33,0:32:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the big headline makers in today's news
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate less than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.33,0:32:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very difficult for people to become realistic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.33,0:32:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in how to handle those kind of energies,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.33,0:32:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the downside of that has shown itself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.33,0:32:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last couple of world wars, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,where the inability of somebody who lives up here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:33:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to even comprehend that it's down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You sign a peace treaty with Adolf Hitler,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.86,0:33:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you go back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.86,0:33:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.86,0:33:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.86,0:33:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.86,0:33:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not the only one in our time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.86,0:33:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hitler thinks you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.86,0:33:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,.
